name: Black Leather
comments: Outtake from The Great Rock 'n' Roll Swindle sessions. The only Sex Pistols members involved in the recording were Steve Jones and Paul Cook , and for this reason some people consider it a song by The Professionals rather than by the Sex Pistols. Truth is, Black Leather was written and recorded after the Sex Pisols split but before The Professionals were formed.
